_sText:
A nice map that took me a few days to make. It still needs some polishing up.
What i need is to add cheapness to the water and dim the lights in the t spawn =)
Will be working on version 1.2 later on in the morning, but right now, im off to bed. Enjoy my map, and please post some feedback =)

Oh ya, i have included the .nav file in the zip (yay) =P

EDIT: Added a ReadMe file to the archive - July 22. 09, 2:43 AM

EDIT: I complete version 1.2 i just need to rewrite the .nav file. Wont be long. Files have not yet been updated. I am currently uploading a video for this map to youtube. I will give more information later. - July 22. 09, 3:59 PM

EDIT: Alright, version 1.2 is up, enjoy it and here is the video for it: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=v6Z6hkaqC9U
In 1.2 i have dimmed the t spawn lights, added a water_lod_control, and added a green decorative light inside the glass pyramid at the center. Enjoy!
